WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:03.000
Conversation A.

00:03.000 --> 00:04.500
Can I help you?

00:04.500 --> 00:10.100
Yes, I'm looking for a dress to wear to the school end of term party.

00:10.100 --> 00:11.600
I see.

00:11.600 --> 00:14.800
All our party dresses are over here.

00:14.800 --> 00:18.800
Would you like a long dress or a short dress?

00:18.800 --> 00:21.280
Uh, short, I think.

00:21.280 --> 00:23.520
This blue dress is nice.

00:23.520 --> 00:25.240
Do you have a size eight?

00:25.240 --> 00:26.240
Yes.

00:26.240 --> 00:27.840
Here you are.

00:27.840 --> 00:29.760
Would you like to try it on?

00:29.760 --> 00:30.760
Thanks.

00:30.760 --> 00:33.960
The changing room is just over there.

00:33.960 --> 00:36.520
Would you like to try anything else on?

00:36.520 --> 00:37.520
Yes.

00:37.520 --> 00:40.120
I'd like to try this red dress as well.

00:40.120 --> 00:41.120
Thanks a lot.

00:41.120 --> 00:42.760
You're welcome.

00:42.760 --> 00:45.080
If you need any help, just ask.

